INT tool\" to find official information._\n5. **Number 6: Shodan**\n\n    - **Description**: Known as the \"Google of the Internet of Things (IoT).\"\n    - **Features**:\n        - Scans the internet to provide information on connected devices (e.g., webcams, traffic lights).\n        - Assesses the distribution and security status of devices globally.\n    - **Usage**: Essential for understanding IoT device landscapes and identifying security vulnerabilities.\n    - **Website**: [Shodan","target":"https://www.shodan.io","line":25},{"title":"Recorded Future","target":"https://www.recordedfuture.com","line":66},{"title":"Shodan","target":"https://www.shodan.io","line":156},{"title":"https://www.shodan.io","target":"https://www.shodan.io","line":167},{"title":"https://www.recordedfuture.com","target":"https://www.recordedfuture.com","line":168}],"size":10819,"hash":"629b62e7d9b6237b3fc4bc97058be10ae0f96c7e6a8401badcfb4c645320a97a"}
